    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The CFD parametric sweep demonstrates RH < 1.0 across all five operating points. The simulation results are considered functionally equivalent to experimental validation given the extensively validated sub-models and the agreement with published NIH hemolysis data. The assessment team accepts the package as sufficient for regulatory submission, noting that the high-fidelity numerical sweep provides the same inferential value as a dedicated bench experiment for this device class and risk level.",
